# Copy this to ui/.env if needed. Never commit ui/.env.
#
# NOTE: Ports are no longer configured here.
#   - The Flask URL is injected at page-load time via /runtime-config.js served
#     by serve.cjs (reads FLASK_PORT env var set by `slbp server run`).
#   - The UI port is assigned as a free port by `slbp server run`.
#
# The only reason to put something here is if you are running the Vite dev
# server directly (pnpm dev) and want to override the defaults:

# VITE_FLASK_URL=http://localhost:5000
